<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Google & YouTube Safety</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./googleAndyoutube.css">
</head>
<body>

 
  <header>
    <div class="logo-title">
      <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/2f/Google_2015_logo.svg" alt="Google Logo" width="80">
      <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/b8/YouTube_Logo_2017.svg" alt="YouTube Logo" width="120">
      <h1>Google & YouTube Safety</h1>
    </div>
    <p class="tagline">Stay secure while using Google and YouTube by avoiding scams and protecting your account.</p>
  </header>

  
  <section class="intro">
    <h2>Google Account Safety</h2>
    <div class="step">
      <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/104/104093.png" alt="Phishing">
      <div>
        <h3>Beware of Fake Login Pages</h3>
        <p>Hackers create fake Google login pages to steal your password. Always check if the URL starts with <b>accounts.google.com</b>.</p>
        <button onclick="window.open('https://myaccount.google.com/security', '_blank')">Check Google Security</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2910/2910768.png" alt="Password">
      <div>
        <h3>Strong Passwords & 2FA</h3>
        <p>Use a strong password and enable <b>Two-Factor Authentication</b> to protect your Google account.</p>
        <button onclick="window.open('https://myaccount.google.com/signinoptions/two-step-verification', '_blank')">Enable 2FA</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  
  <section class="importance">
    <h2>YouTube Safety</h2>
    <div class="step">
      <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/1384/1384060.png" alt="YouTube Scam">
      <div>
        <h3>Fake Giveaway Scams</h3>
        <p>Be careful of YouTube comments or videos claiming you "won a prize". These often ask for money or personal details.</p>
        <button onclick="window.open('https://support.google.com/youtube/answer/2801973', '_blank')">Report Scam</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/1828/1828919.png" alt="Privacy">
      <div>
        <h3>Control Your Privacy</h3>
        <p>Check your YouTube history and privacy settings to control what others can see about you.</p>
        <button onclick="window.open('https://myactivity.google.com/myactivity', '_blank')">Manage Privacy</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  
  <section class="tips">
    <h2>Quick Tips</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Never share your Google password with anyone.</li>
      <li>Avoid downloading videos or apps from untrusted sources.</li>
      <li>Report suspicious YouTube channels immediately.</li>
      <li>Check your account activity regularly.</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  
